lines.text: let n be a long integer
let x1 , x2 , y1 , y2 be long integers
lines.code: long long x1 , x2 , y1 , y2 ;

lines.text: let sum be a long integer with sum = 0 , a = 2d array of long integers with 110 rows and 110 columns
for long integer k = 0 to n exclusive
lines.code: for ( long long k = 0 ; k < n ; k ++ )

lines.text: for long integer i = x1 to x2 inclusive
lines.code: for ( long long i = x1 ; i <= x2 ; i ++ )

lines.text: for long integer j = y1 to y2 inclusive , increment a [ i ] [ j ] by 1
lines.code: for ( long long j = y1 ; j <= y2 ; j ++ ) { a [ i ] [ j ] ++ ; }

lines.text: for long integer i = 1 to 100 inclusive
lines.code: for ( long long i = 1 ; i <= 100 ; i ++ )

lines.text: for long integer j = 1 to 100 inclusive , sum = sum + a [ i ] [ j ]
lines.code: for ( long long j = 1 ; j <= 100 ; j ++ ) { sum += a [ i ] [ j ] ; }
